name: Conte Enegy Evolution
description:
Get ready for the ultimate Lode Runner experience with new levels, these levels are so hard that will make your brain melt, in most of the situations you need to use game glitches, bugs, enemy AI, and enemy revive location + many other tricks in order to solve all the game puzzles.

  * all the levels have been tested and completed successfully.
  * most of the levels are from the game Championship Lode Runner and the hacks Lode Runner Blue and Miku Runner.
  * when enemies takes the energy coins they change color.
  * graphics from the Conte Enegy bootleg game.
  * only for master players.
